# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge

We pledge to be respectful and inclusive, and to foster a community where everyone feels welcome.

## Our Standards

- Be respectful.
- No harassment.
- Focus on what is best for the community.
- Be open to feedback.

## Enforcement

Instances of unacceptable behaviour can be reported to [chides2012@gmail.com].

## Attribution

This Code of Conduct is adapted from the [Contributor Covenant][homepage], version 2.0.
